column2: select cam.*,p.attr_value   from cancer_study cs    left outer join clinical_attribute_meta cam     on cam.cancer_study_id=cs.cancer_study_id --   and cam.attr_id =&&&    left outer join patient p      on p.internal_id=cam.patient_id     and p.attr_id=cam.attr_id  where cs.cancer_study_identifier=&&&
